ackModal_main_3613101\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Jan 13, 2025</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104fre1665702639431.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/fre1665702639431.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/fre1665702639431.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"fre1665702639431\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Hover View (HoverView)\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">This property determines whether the contents of a field are displayed in a tool tip when the cursor is positioned over the field.\n </p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"fre1665702639431__p_d104693e1_d104694e1_d104695e1\">HoverView<code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code><code class=\"ph codeph defvalue\">False</code> | <code class=\"ph codeph\">True</code></p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"fre1665702639431__p_d104696e1_d104697e1_d104698e1\">The size and duration of the tooltip can be configured in <span class=\"ph filepath\">usys.ini</span>:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">[application]\ntooltip = utooltip(maxwidth=<var class=\"keyword varname\">Pixels</var>;duration=<var class=\"keyword varname\">Seconds</var>)</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"fre1665702639431__table_d12362e1_d12363e1_d12364e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"fre1665702639431__table_d12362e1_d12363e1_d12364e1__entry__1\">\n Value\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"fre1665702639431__table_d12362e1_d12363e1_d12364e1__entry__2\">\n Description\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fre1665702639431__table_d12362e1_d12363e1_d12364e1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">True</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fre1665702639431__table_d12362e1_d12363e1_d12364e1__entry__2\">\n Displays the contents of a Picture or Edit Box widget when the cursor hovers over the field.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fre1665702639431__table_d12362e1_d12363e1_d12364e1__entry__1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph defvalue\">False</code>  (default) </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fre1665702639431__table_d12362e1_d12363e1_d12364e1__entry__2\">\n No effect.\n </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"fre1665702639431__section_z53_mjd_xwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d218998e124\">Usage</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"fre1665702639431__table_d12365e1_d12366e1_d12367e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"> Dynamic? </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"> Yes </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"> Supported in Grid? </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"> Yes </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"> Dependencies: </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"> Not applicable if\n                           <code class=\"ph codeph\">ToolTipText=</code>True</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"fre1665702639431__section_gkn_pjd_xwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d218998e174\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"fre1665702639431__p_d104705e1_d104706e1_d104707e1\">The <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Hover View</span> property is\n            especially useful when used in a grid or multi-occurrence list that contains fields that\n            cannot be completely displayed.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"fre1665702639431__p_d104708e1_d104709e1_d104710e1\">When set to <code class=\"ph codeph\">True</code>:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"fre1665702639431__ul_rnn_qjd_xwb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"fre1665702639431__li_d41819e1_d41820e1_d41821e1\">In an Edit Box widget, the field contents start\n               to wrap when the maxwidth has been reached. The height of the field is automatically\n               adjusted to fit the text. </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"fre1665702639431__li_d41822e1_d41823e1_d41824e1\">In a Picture widget, the resulting tool tip\n               displays the complete image in a window that has the same aspect ratio as the image.\n            </li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"note tip note_tip\" id=\"fre1665702639431__note_tnn_qjd_xwb\"><span class=\"note__title\">Tip:</span> The <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Hover View</span> property is\n            not recommended for fields that contain a lot of data. In this case, it may be better to\n            use the <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Tool Tip Text</span> property, which is limited to 1024 bytes.\n            If both properties are set, the <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Tool Tip Text</span> is used.</div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"fre1665702639431__section_b3v_qjd_xwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d218998e213\">Example: Setting in ProcScript </h2>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"fre1665702639431__pre_sh1_sjd_xwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">$fieldproperties(FLD1) = \"hoverview=true\"</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"fre1665702639431__section_jnd_sjd_xwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d218998e222\">Example: Configuring Hover View</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"fre1665702639431__p_d104717e1_d104718e1_d104719e1\">To control the size of tool tips and how long they\n            are displayed, set properties for <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">tooltip</span> in the [application]\n            section of the <span class=\"ph filepath\">usys.ini</span> file. For example:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"fre1665702639431__pre_ad4_tjd_xwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">[application]\ntooltip = utooltip(maxwidth=200;duration=5)</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"fre1665702639431__p_d104720e1_d104721e1_d104722e1\">This sets the width of the tooltip to 200 pixels\n            and displays the tooltip after the cursor has hovered over a field for 5 seconds.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"fre1665702639431__section_exr_tjd_xwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d218998e243\">Applies To</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"fre1665702639431__ul_pkp_vjd_xwb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"fre1665702639431__li_d41825e1_d41826e1_d41827e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"klb1688454363706.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/klb1688454363706.html\" title=\"Default logical widget for entering and displaying data in a field in a Form or Report.\">EditBox</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"fre1665702639431__li_d41828e1_d41829e1_d41830e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"lxc1665703126500.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/lxc1665703126500.html\" title=\"The upicture widget is used to displays the contents of an Image field. Uniface provides a logical widget called Picture, which is mapped to upicture.\">upicture (Picture)</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/gbk1665702628600.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Tool Tip Text (ToolTipText)</a><p>This property specifies the text to be displayed when the cursor is positioned over the widget. It can be a string up to 1024 bytes.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ibm1665703257495.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Tooltip</a><p>Control the size and length of time tool tips are displayed, for widget that support tooltips.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3613101\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3613101\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Hover View (HoverView) Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Jan 13, 2025 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Hover View (HoverView) This property determines whether the contents of a field are displayed in a tool tip when the cursor is positioned over the field. HoverView = False | True The size and duration of the tooltip can be configured in usys.ini : [application] tooltip = utooltip(maxwidth= Pixels ;duration= Seconds ) Copy Value Description True Displays the contents of a Picture or Edit Box widget when the cursor hovers over the field. False (default) No effect. Usage Dynamic? Yes Supported in Grid? Yes Dependencies: Not applicable if ToolTipText= True Description The Hover View property is especially useful when used in a grid or multi-occurrence list that contains fields that cannot be completely displayed. When set to True : In an Edit Box widget, the field contents start to wrap when the maxwidth has been reached. The height of the field is automatically adjusted to fit the text. In a Picture widget, the resulting tool tip displays the complete image in a window that has the same aspect ratio as the image. Tip: The Hover View property is not recommended for fields that contain a lot of data. In this case, it may be better to use the Tool Tip Text property, which is limited to 1024 bytes. If both properties are set, the Tool Tip Text is used. Example: Setting in ProcScript $fieldproperties(FLD1) = \"hoverview=true\" Copy Example: Configuring Hover View To control the size of tool tips and how long they are displayed, set properties for tooltip in the [application] section of the usys.ini file. For example: [application] tooltip = utooltip(maxwidth=200;duration=5) Copy This sets the width of the tooltip to 200 pixels and displays the tooltip after the cursor has hovered over a field for 5 seconds. Applies To EditBox upicture (Picture) Related Links Tool Tip Text (ToolTipText) This property specifies the text to be displayed when the cursor is positioned over the widget. It can be a string up to 1024 bytes. Tooltip Control the size and length of time tool tips are displayed, for widget that support tooltips. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}